Title: Part 6: The white city
Text:
After Saruman is defeated, I must go to Gondor and warn the people. The Palanntir of Saruman showed the planned attack of Sauron on Minas Tirith.
The people of Gondor need support!
CompleteText:
Here it is...the white city!

I should go to the Hall of Kings at the top!Saruman is defeated now, but his Palanntir showed a planned attack of Sauron on Minas Tirith, so I have to warn them!
